explanations.text: Javadoc-style comments used to document code, often including tags such as @param, @return, and @author.

The pattern involves documentation or metadata tags in code, typically starting with \"@\", \"@param\", \"@return\", \"@var\", \"@type\", \"@author\", \"@license\", \"@see\", \"@brief\", \"@ingroup\",
